reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Reliable Drives, But Slow Write Speeds and No Activity Light
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased a 3-pack of these SanDisk Ultra 32GB flash drives. They have a nice compact design that slides easily onto a keychain or in a pocket. The USB 3.0 interface means fast data transfer speeds when using USB 3.0 ports.However, I was disappointed to find the write speeds limited to USB 2.0 speeds, even when plugged into USB 3.0 ports. Saving large files seems to crawl compared to reads. There is also no LED activity light, so you don't know when data is transferring.That said, the read speeds are fast, allowing quick access to media and documents. The drives feel well-constructed and sturdy. And you can't beat getting 3 drives for the price.Overall, the drives work reliably and I'd purchase them again for the convenience of having multiple flash drives. But the slow write speeds and lack of activity indicator prevent this from being a 5 star product. I'm taking off 1 star for those shortcomings, so 4 stars from me.

reviews.reviewTitle: Compact Powerhouse - SanDisk 32GB Ultra USB 3.0 Flash Drive
reviews.reviewText: The SanDisk 32GB Ultra USB 3.0 Flash Drive has been an absolute game-changer for me. As someone who frequently works with large files and needs a reliable storage solution, this flash drive has exceeded all my expectations.Firstly, the storage capacity is perfect for everyday use. 32GB is ample space for storing a variety of files, be it high-resolution photos, documents, videos, or music. It's the ideal size for both personal and professional use, striking the right balance between capacity and portability.Speed is where this flash drive truly shines. The USB 3.0 interface offers incredibly fast data transfer rates. I was amazed at how quickly it can move large files compared to older USB 2.0 drives. This efficiency saves a significant amount of time, especially when I'm working with tight deadlines.The build quality of the SanDisk Ultra is commendable. It's sturdy and durable, yet compact and sleek. The retractable design is a thoughtful touch, protecting the USB connector when not in use and eliminating the need for a separate cap that can be easily lost. Its small size makes it extremely portable, fitting easily in a pocket or on a keychain.What’s more, the compatibility of this flash drive is impressive. It works seamlessly with various operating systems and devices, making it a versatile tool for different tech ecosystems. This universal compatibility is a huge plus for someone like me who works across multiple platforms.The value for money is another standout aspect. For its features and performance, the price is very reasonable. It’s an investment that offers reliability and efficiency without breaking the bank.In summary, the SanDisk 32GB Ultra USB 3.0 Flash Drive is an outstanding product. Whether you’re a professional needing quick file transfers or someone looking for a dependable storage solution, this flash drive won’t disappoint. It's fast, reliable, and offers excellent value, making it deserving of a 5-star rating.

reviews.reviewTitle: Solution de stockage fiable et performante, je conseil !!
reviews.reviewText: En tant que photographe professionnel, j'accorde une grande importance à la qualité et à la fiabilité de mes outils de stockage. La clé USB SanDisk Ultra 32 Go s'est avérée être un choix excellent pour mes besoins. Elle offre une vitesse de transfert très satisfaisante, ce qui me permet de gérer efficacement mes fichiers de photos de grande taille. Cette rapidité est particulièrement appréciable dans le cadre de mon travail, où l'efficacité est primordiale. Avec ses 32 Go de capacité, je trouve assez d'espace pour stocker mes projets en cours sans souci. Sa robustesse est également un point fort, résistant bien à l'usage quotidien et aux déplacements fréquents. C'est un aspect crucial pour moi qui suis souvent en déplacement.Globalement, la clé USB SanDisk Ultra 32 Go est une solution de stockage fiable et performante, que je recommanderais sans hésiter à d'autres professionnels dans le domaine de la photographie.
